    <h1>GOD IS W.O.R.D. #2</h1>
    <h2>Welcome, come one and come all!</h2>
    <p>
      Greetings the in the name of the Lord Jesus Christ, the Son of the Living God.
      We want to welcome you to our second edition of "GOD IS W.O.R.D." where we explore the Word of God not just as a book, but as the living and active presence of God in our lives.
    Join us as we delve deeper into the Scriptures and discover the transformative power of God's Word. 
  </p>
  <br>
  <h2>What is W.O.R.D.?</h2>
  <p>W.O.R.D. stands for "Word OutReach Deliverance." It signifies our commitment to understanding the Scriptures as a source of divine revelation and guidance in our lives.
    Through living it in our daily lives, we aim to embody the teachings of the Bible and share its message with others.
  </p>
  <br>
  <h2>Join Us</h2>
  <p>We invite you to join us for this transformative journey as we seek to grow in our understanding of God's Word and its application in our lives.
    Together, let us explore the depths of Scripture and experience the life-changing power of God's truth.
  Stay tuned for more updates and resources as we continue this journey together.
  </p>
  <br>
  <h2>Services and Hours</h2>
  <p>Join us for our weekly services:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Sundays at 12 PM - Worship Service</li>
    <li>Mondays at 7:00 PM - Prayer Meeting</li>
    <li>Wednesdays at 7:00 PM - Bible Study</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We look forward to seeing you there!</p>
  <br>    
